                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/4911.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Douglas, Ariz.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-09-13T11:00:00-07:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 13, 1912—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mexican Federal commander at Aguaprieta informs me that rebels went south last
                    night about 11 o’clock.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dye.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
